data.description: Welcome to your future haven in the sought-after SW Cape Coral neighborhood, where luxury and comfort converge in this stunning residence. This property stands out with its large, landscaped yard, offering privacy and an inviting ambiance.  Upon entering through the screened front door, you'll be captivated by the expansive layout, centering around a large, modern kitchen - a chef's dream and perfect for entertaining. The open-plan design integrates the living area with the kitchen, ensuring a seamless flow for gatherings.  Step outside to the screened lanai, an ideal spot to relax, protected by hurricane screens for added safety. The backyard, spacious and fenced, provides ample room for a pool, making it a potential oasis for Florida's sunny days.  Each bedroom, especially the master suite, offers a serene retreat with comfort and style. The home's location is a major plus, situated close to parks, shopping, dining, and entertainment options, blending tranquility with convenience.  This property is more than a home; it's a lifestyle choice, offering a balance of luxury, comfort, and convenience. Don’t miss the opportunity to make this dream home yours.
